  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Grazax in Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase III Trial Investigating the Efficacy and Safety of Grazax in Children Aged 5-16 Years With Grass Pollen Induced Rhinoconjunctivitis With or Without Asthma</official_title>
