  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate if immunotherapy with Grazax is safe and reduces
      the hayfever symptoms and the use of symptom relieving medications in children during the
      grass pollen season
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
